        "content": "<p>For completeness, was able to combine the two proofs to show <code>6 |</code> which in the end was really straight forward once I remembered I actually had to establish that 2 and 3 are coprime!</p>\n<p>(Still want to figure out the <code>3k + {0,1,2}</code> approach for <code>3 |</code> but will come back to it)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/xaviershay/lean-proofs/blob/main/LeanProofs/Basic.lean\">https://github.com/xaviershay/lean-proofs/blob/main/LeanProofs/Basic.lean</a></p>\n<p>Thank you everyone for your assistance!</p>",
